> Still [observing](https://cirrus-ci.com/task/5188905141010432) a memory usage [spike](https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/24531#issuecomment-1072210898) up to 25.38 GB.

It appears, that those spikes are caused by recursive usage of `RPCResult`. The applied refactoring has removed them.

@sipsorcery Is this bug familiar to you?
